data.description: Discover a beautifully remodeled bungalow, perfectly situated just a short stroll away from the Al Weeks Sr. beach access in the charming historic district of Ormond by the Sea. This beach-side abode has undergone an extensive transformation, rendering it completely move-in ready, with minimal maintenance required for its newer metal roof. Notable updates include a 2017 AC replacement, and in 2023, new ceiling fans were thoughtfully added. Luxury vinyl plank flooring graces every room, creating a seamless and elegant aesthetic throughout. The galley kitchen, though modest in size, shines with granite countertops, new cabinets, a stylish backsplash, a refrigerator, and updated fixtures. Opening up to two distinct yet equally bright and spacious living areas, the remodeled kitchen provides a welcoming heart for this home. The bathroom showcases a new vanity, sink, and fixtures, adding to the overall sense of modernity. Indoor laundry facilities are conveniently located just off the kitchen, making daily chores a breeze. Additional storage space can be found in the attached closet off the carport. The oversized backyard is fenced in, offering both privacy and a private outdoor shower, which is accessible from the remodeled sun-room or laundry room. This unique home truly offers a slice of paradise, perfect for coastal living and enjoying the Florida sunshine.
